HEADWORD: disseminative
<hw>dis*sem"i*na*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Tending to
disseminate, or to become disseminated.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

